Do you know what people call that?

517
00:46:54,880 --> 00:46:57,700
It is called an automatic protective mechanism.

518
00:46:57,740 --> 00:47:01,630
Your own self is more precious than love.

519
00:47:01,630 --> 00:47:05,930
You've come to realize that after experiencing multiple heartbreaks.

520
00:47:08,600 --> 00:47:10,500
Seems like it.

521
00:47:22,060 --> 00:47:25,820
There's a meeting tomorrow to decide about the concert location.

522
00:47:36,580 --> 00:47:38,450
Yeah, Jeong Mi?

523
00:47:39,850 --> 00:47:42,630
Na Yeong just went into surgery.

524
00:47:43,130 --> 00:47:45,780
Tell the guys that she's okay.

525
00:47:49,220 --> 00:47:53,380
Thanks to her, I had free time to think.

526
00:48:13,000 --> 00:48:14,750
Thank you.

527
00:48:14,750 --> 00:48:16,920
Hurry and leave for your work.

528
00:48:16,940 --> 00:48:18,520
Okay.

529
00:48:32,250 --> 00:48:34,080
I'm sorry, Seo Hoo.

530
00:48:36,660 --> 00:48:38,320
How can you be late for an important meeting?

531
00:48:38,370 --> 00:48:40,840
I saw the message for the change of meeting time, late.

532
00:48:40,840 --> 00:48:42,430
Do you know how many times I called you?

533
00:48:42,430 --> 00:48:44,160
It was a meeting to decide location for the concert.

534
00:48:44,160 --> 00:48:45,660
You should have been there as the person in charge.

535
00:48:45,660 --> 00:48:48,340
- Do you know how important this is to us?
- Seo Hoo.

536
00:48:48,340 --> 00:48:51,770
We probably have to look for another place for the concert.

537
00:49:50,330 --> 00:49:52,080
Are you sleeping?

538
00:49:52,950 --> 00:49:56,260
I just came and laid down.

539
00:49:56,790 --> 00:49:58,730
You worked hard yesterday.

540
00:49:58,770 --> 00:50:00,860
Is Na Yeong doing well?

541
00:50:00,860 --> 00:50:03,670
The surgery ended well.

542
00:50:03,670 --> 00:50:09,390
Yesterday when she suddenly called during dinner saying how much it hurt, I was so shocked.

543
00:50:11,270 --> 00:50:14,090
Your voice has no strength.

544
00:50:15,490 --> 00:50:18,310
I'm so tired.

545
00:50:18,350 --> 00:50:20,360
There must have been a lot of work.

546
00:50:20,400 --> 00:50:23,090
I'm so tired.

547
00:50:25,040 --> 00:50:27,480
Okay, I'll hang up. Go sleep.

548
00:50:27,530 --> 00:50:30,170
I can't sleep yet.

549
00:50:30,850 --> 00:50:32,990
I need to wipe off my makeup.

550
00:50:34,220 --> 00:50:36,860
It's so tiring.

551
00:50:36,860 --> 00:50:39,010
Every morning, I have to do makeup

552
00:50:39,010 --> 00:50:41,150
and remove it.

553
00:50:43,020 --> 00:50:46,390
I wish someone would remove my makeup for me.

554
00:50:47,590 --> 00:50:49,720
How do you remove it?

555
00:50:50,570 --> 00:50:53,000
You don't even do makeup.

556
00:50:54,070 --> 00:50:55,950
What would you do if you knew how to?

557
00:50:55,990 --> 00:50:58,000
Well, whenever...

558
00:50:58,030 --> 00:51:00,460
You never know when you'll need it.

559
00:51:05,140 --> 00:51:06,860
First...

560
00:51:09,560 --> 00:51:12,660
You need two makeup pads

561
00:51:19,400 --> 00:51:23,120
and soak eye (makeup) remover on that.

562
00:51:25,590 --> 00:51:29,690
Then place them on the eyelids for a short while.

563
00:51:45,900 --> 00:51:49,780
After a short while, you gently wipe them off.

564
00:52:11,770 --> 00:52:13,420
Next,

565
00:52:14,290 --> 00:52:16,560
using another pad,

566
00:52:16,630 --> 00:52:18,990
wipe lipstick off.

567
00:52:24,370 --> 00:52:26,070
Like this?

568
00:52:26,720 --> 00:52:27,910
Yeah.

569
00:52:27,950 --> 00:52:30,980
Do it lightly so wrinkles don't form.

570
00:52:38,110 --> 00:52:39,690
And then?

571
00:52:40,190 --> 00:52:43,190
Apply cleansing cream onto my face

572
00:52:43,870 --> 00:52:45,960
and using your fingertips,

573
00:52:45,960 --> 00:52:49,670
massage all over the face.

574
00:53:13,620 --> 00:53:16,250
It feels good.

575
00:53:20,110 --> 00:53:24,230
After that, wipe gently with a tissue.

576
00:53:34,680 --> 00:53:37,320
Softly and meticulously.

577
00:53:53,190 --> 00:53:58,060
It's so good when you have someone next to you to remove your makeup.

578
00:53:59,000 --> 00:54:01,090
It's really good.

579
00:54:23,490 --> 00:54:26,860
It's awkward since it's been a while.

580
00:54:34,000 --> 00:54:37,900
Love you

581
00:54:46,180 --> 00:54:50,730
The Time I've Loved You...

582
00:55:00,630 --> 00:55:06,280
I am sorry I was late at the meeting yesterday because of personal matters.

583
00:55:06,280 --> 00:55:09,940
Please reconsider our use of the place.

584
00:55:09,940 --> 00:55:13,630
I am sorry but the date that Cha Seo Hoo wants to reserve  the place

585
00:55:13,630 --> 00:55:18,530
was double booked in error. But the decision was made yesterday for the other party.

586
00:55:18,530 --> 00:55:22,490
We can reschedule the concert.

587
00:55:24,160 --> 00:55:27,820
I heard the owner of this restaurant is interested not only in classical music,

588
00:55:27,820 --> 00:55:31,510
but also in World Vision and foreign volunteer work as well.

589
00:55:31,520 --> 00:55:35,480
I see that you know a lot about my father.

590
00:55:35,480 --> 00:55:39,610
So I want to make an offer.

591
00:56:23,680 --> 00:56:26,620
I was surprised to hear that you wanted to see me here.

592
00:56:26,620 --> 00:56:32,400
How do I cheer you up after being angry like that yesterday? I was worried about it.

593
00:56:34,370 --> 00:56:39,660
I got the outdoor concert location rescheduled.

594
00:56:39,660 --> 00:56:41,490
Is that so?

595
00:56:42,800 --> 00:56:46,670
In the end, Oh Ha Na made it happen.

596
00:56:48,760 --> 00:56:54,980
There were a few conditions left to be mediated, but the performance will go as planned.

597
00:56:54,980 --> 00:56:57,740
That's good news.

598
00:57:03,990 --> 00:57:12,540
In this place, I thought about loving you again.

599
00:57:13,480 --> 00:57:14,970
Is that so?

600
00:57:14,970 --> 00:57:19,920
When the concert was cancelled, the image of your back, looking at this empty hall...

601
00:57:19,920 --> 00:57:25,410
I said I wouldn't lose you again.

602
00:57:25,430 --> 00:57:30,430
I realized, "Ah, I still haven't forgotten about this person."

603
00:57:31,420 --> 00:57:34,200
"This person's back

604
00:57:35,530 --> 00:57:38,610
is hurting."

605
00:57:39,960 --> 00:57:43,660
"I want to be with Cha Seo Hoo again."

606
00:57:51,050 --> 00:57:56,030
Is that your answer to my marriage proposal?

607
00:58:02,290 --> 00:58:06,200
I'm sorry, Seo Hoo.

608
00:58:13,770 --> 00:58:17,310
I don't think I can do this anymore.

609
00:58:17,310 --> 00:58:19,970
What?

610
00:58:19,970 --> 00:58:23,160
What could you not do?

611
00:58:28,230 --> 00:58:32,430
Surely, as we continue to fight

612
00:58:32,430 --> 00:58:39,160
and hate each other, we will slowly get tired of this.

613
00:58:41,120 --> 00:58:43,780
For this reason, let's end this now.

614
00:58:45,140 --> 00:58:49,650
So we can remember it as a love that made our hearts flutter,

615
00:58:51,220 --> 00:58:54,490
let's break up. Okay?

616
00:58:59,440 --> 00:59:04,300
No. I can't do that.

617
00:59:04,320 --> 00:59:06,480
You just have to come back.

618
00:59:06,480 --> 00:59:09,680
- I'm sorry, Seo Hoo.
- Oh Ha Na!

619
00:59:09,680 --> 00:59:15,150
I'm sorry. Sorry, Seo Hoo.

620
01:00:03,370 --> 01:00:07,990
That passion and the one that I longed for...

621
01:00:07,990 --> 01:00:13,660
That fever-like love has come to its end.

622
01:00:42,390 --> 01:00:49,530
Timing and Subtitles brought to you by The Timeless Lovers @ Viki

623
01:00:54,160 --> 01:00:56,510
On this side will be the food table.

624
01:00:56,510 --> 01:01:00,460
Over here is where the stage will be, so if you could just pull the tables further—

625
01:01:00,460 --> 01:01:02,430
Excuse me.

626
01:01:04,470 --> 01:01:08,660
- Cha Seo Hoo just called saying he'll arrive soon.
- I see.

627
01:01:08,660 --> 01:01:13,800
He said he prepared a surprise event for the one in-charge of performance advertising.

628
01:01:50,290 --> 01:01:51,490
It's Cha Seo Hoo!

629
01:02:29,230 --> 01:02:33,910
The script where it stopped on "I will never love you" and didn't have an ending yet...

630
01:02:33,910 --> 01:02:36,950
I have started on it again.

631
01:02:39,760 --> 01:02:43,240
The Time I've Loved You...
Seventeen years later, the present

632
01:02:43,240 --> 01:02:45,620
Scene 99.
[Beach]

633
01:02:55,620 --> 01:03:01,320
If you are crying, I can find you wherever you are.

634
01:03:02,590 --> 01:03:08,130
Even in the moments you can't remember, I was always by your side.

635
01:03:11,590 --> 01:03:15,540
The next part of the script that I was going to write...

636
01:03:15,540 --> 01:03:18,140
Aren't you curious about it?

637
01:03:29,800 --> 01:03:33,930
If we meet again like a habit or not...

638
01:03:33,930 --> 01:03:36,160
Do you want to make a bet?

639
01:03:38,300 --> 01:03:40,660
Come to me now.

640
01:03:55,750 --> 01:03:57,230
Won.

641
01:03:57,230 --> 01:04:04,340
♬ I will be right beside you. ♬

642
01:04:04,380 --> 01:04:12,610
♬ But you always are gazing at a distant place. ♬

643
01:04:12,610 --> 01:04:15,760
♬ The words which are always hovering somewhere in my heart ♬

644
01:04:15,760 --> 01:04:18,370
- Do you really have a person you like?
- Yes.

645
01:04:18,370 --> 01:04:19,930
Scouting offer?

646
01:04:19,950 --> 01:04:23,830
I recommended you to be in-charge of the marketing team in the office in Paris, France.

647
01:04:23,890 --> 01:04:26,670
You're coming to me with a counter offer? As expected, you're smart.

648
01:04:26,690 --> 01:04:28,450
Oh Ha Na's decision is a priority.

649
01:04:28,450 --> 01:04:32,240
There are times where my heart fluttered because of you, and I like being together.

650
01:04:32,240 --> 01:04:34,240
I thought it was special.

651
01:04:34,240 --> 01:04:37,600
I am thinking of putting you in-charge of Cha Seo Hoo's performances.

652
01:04:37,600 --> 01:04:38,910
What do you mean?

653
01:04:38,910 --> 01:04:43,890
I mean to say that you become a professional who puts work first, before love.

654
01:04:44,820 --> 01:04:48,830
It's alright if you're late. I don't mind waiting.
